{
  "stem": "16140.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they made a uprising in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, her Father gave a lot of money to buy ammunition and all kinds of stuff to fight against the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ghetto, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, I wasn't in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I know that they were fighting back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had the papers done [? there ?] to Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, they worked for the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Nazis always ordered, they wanted money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sometimes they wanted valuables.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sometimes they wanted people. to say they're taking them to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, they were killing them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's what all what the Judenrat did, collecting valuables from Jewish people, giving it to the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They collect from everybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know about that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother was dealing with that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A day before the liberation some-- some-- some soldiers were killing the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't the Nazis, it was other soldiers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Partisans.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, a lot of-- a lot of the Bandera group, those were fighting for independence Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of those Bandera group were killing Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] That's a good question.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's-- they were doing it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some young people, some older people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a day before the liberation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A lot of Jewish people got killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1944",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Can't remember.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I mean, we-- we knew that they were killed, so we imagine it was the Bandera group, because they were killing Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we actually don't know which partisans killed them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some partisans killed them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went to [INAUDIBLE], and then we met-- were met by the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a village.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the leader of the Russian army was a Jewish general.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was half Jewish, half Russian, Boris Lebdavidov.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he-- he liberated us.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
